				href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iterative_and_incremental_development&amp;sa=D&amp;source=editors&amp;ust=1682924986928466&amp;usg=AOvVaw3D12wWrrCcE46mlnQAMUsn">Iterative
